    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The clock is ticking, and there’s only <i>Five Minutes Till Christmas!</i> Step into the holiday frenzy as you race through the bustling halls of the local shopping mall, dashing to fulfill every last gift request. The stakes are high—everyone’s Christmas joy rests in your hands, and there’s no time to waste!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330390/extras/b4228a852fd37ae5ec0390455396438a.poster.avif?t=1734336271\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330390/extras/b4228a852fd37ae5ec0390455396438a.webm?t=1734336271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330390/extras/b4228a852fd37ae5ec0390455396438a.mp4?t=1734336271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But it won’t be easy. Security guards are on high alert, keeping an eye out for anyone moving a little too fast or getting a little too creative with their shortcuts. Every gift you grab boosts your score, but getting caught could mean missing out on the perfect Christmas for everyone on your list. You’ll need speed, wits, and a keen sense of strategy to avoid detection and make it out in time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330390/extras/f82758a91d31e04dde27c127d7bdf0a3.poster.avif?t=1734336271\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330390/extras/f82758a91d31e04dde27c127d7bdf0a3.webm?t=1734336271\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330390/extras/f82758a91d31e04dde27c127d7bdf0a3.mp4?t=1734336271\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the five minutes are up, your performance will be scored, showing just how well you spread the holiday cheer. And with global leaderboards, you can compare your skills against others, proving who really has what it takes to make it a merry Christmas. Are you ready to beat the clock and save the holiday season?</p>",
